==English==

===Etymology===
Recorded since 1340. From {{etyl|la}} {{term|quotidianus|quotīdiānus|everyday|lang=la}} < {{term|quotidie|quotīdiē|daily|lang=la}}, itself from {{term|quot||how many|lang=la}} + {{term|dies|diēs|day|lang=la}}

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|/kwɒˈtɪdɪən/}}
* {{audio|en-us-quotidian.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# [[daily]]; [[occurring]] or [[recurring]] every [[day]].
# [[common]], [[ordinary]], [[trivial]].

